<!doctype html>

<html>
<head>
	<title>My HCI Friends</title>	
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<script src="js/jquery-1.11.0.js"></script>
	<script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>
	<script src="js/hci-friends.js"></script>
	<link href="css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<link href="css/bootstrap-theme.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<link href="css/hci-friends.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>
	<div class="container">
	<h1>My HCI Friends</h1>

	<div class = "friend">
	<img src="http://lorempixel.com/500/500/people/" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Tony Ton</h3></a>
	<p>Good game player.</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/78/Douglas_Engelbart_in_2008.jpg/972px-Douglas_Engelbart_in_2008.jpg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Doug Engelbart</h3></a>
	<p>Has awesome pet mice</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/5/5c/Ivan_Sutherland_at_CHM.jpg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Ivan Sutherland</h3></a>
	<p>Great at sketching</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/df/Lucy_Suchman.jpeg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Lucy Suchman</h3></a>
	<p>Loves Trukese navigators</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/ea/Vannevar_Bush_portrait.jpg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Vannevar Bush</h3></a>
	<p>Has stellar associative memory</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://amhistory.si.edu/ogmt/images/upload/women-mathematicians/AHB2012q06025.jpg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Grace Hopper</h3></a>
	<p>Only friend with a Navy ship named after them</p>
	<hr>

	<img src="http://uploads.edubilla.com/awards-winners/92/b4/allen-newell.jpg" class="img-responsive">
	<a class="name" href="#"><h3>Allen Newell</h3></a>
	<p>Really into psychology</p>
	</div>
	
	<form id="addFriendForm" role="form" method="get" action="/add">
		<h3>Add a friend</h3>
		
	    <div class="form-group">
	      <label for="name">Name:</label>
	      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Name" name="name">
	    </div>
	    
	    <div class="form-group">
	      <label for="description">Description:</label>
	      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="description" placeholder="Description" name="description">
	    </div>
	    
	    <input type="submit" id="submitBtn" class="btn btn-default" value="Add the friend"></input>
	</form>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
